    &::selection { /* 2 */
      color: #64FFDA;
    }
  }
}
```

```
a {
  b { /* 1 */
    &:hover, .c { /* 2 */
      top: 0;
    }
  }
}
```

The following patterns are not considered problems:

As all of the following pseudo-classes rules would have a nesting depth of just 1.

```
a {
  b { /* 1 */
    &:hover { /* ignored */
      top: 0;
    }
  }
}
```

```
a {
  b { /* 1 */
    &:nest {
      &:nest-lvl2 {  /* ignored */
        top: 0;
      }
    }
  }
}
```

```
a {
  &:hover {  /* ignored */
    b { /* 1 */
      top: 0;
    }
  }
}
```

```
a {
  &:nest {  /* ignored */
    &:nest-lvl2 {  /* ignored */
      top: 0;
      b { /* 1 */
        bottom: 0;
      }
    }
  }
}
```

```
a {
  b { /* 1 */
    &:hover, &:focus {  /* ignored */
      top: 0;
    }
  }
}
```

