  "custom-property-no-missing-var-function": true
}
```

The following patterns are considered problems:

```
:root { --foo: red; }
a { color: --foo; }
```

```
@property --foo {}
a { color: --foo; }
```

The following patterns are not considered problems:

```
:root { --foo: red; }
a { color: var(--foo); }
```

```
@property --foo {}
a { color: var(--foo); }
```

```
@property --foo {}
a { transition-property: --foo; }
```

