## Options[​](#options)

### `"string"`[​](#string)

`@import` rules must always use string notation.

```
{
  "import-notation": "string"
}
```

The following patterns are considered problems:

```
@import url(foo.css);
```

```
@import url('foo.css');
```

```
@import url("foo.css");
```

The following patterns are not considered problems:

```
@import 'foo.css';
```

