@import "foo.css";
```

### `"url"`[​](#url)

`@import` rules must always use URL notation.

```
{
  "import-notation": "url"
}
```

The following patterns are considered problems:

```
@import 'foo.css';
```

```
@import "foo.css";
```

The following patterns are not considered problems:

```
@import url(foo.css);
```

```
@import url('foo.css');
```

```
@import url("foo.css");
```

