## Options[​](#options)

### `Array<string>`[​](#arraystring)

```
["array", "of", "units"]
```

Given:

```
{
  "unit-allowed-list": ["px", "em", "deg"]
}
```

The following patterns are considered problems:

```
a { width: 100%; }
```

```
a { font-size: 10rem; }
```

```
a { animation: animation-name 5s ease; }
```

The following patterns are not considered problems:

```
a { font-size: 1.2em; }
```

```
a { line-height: 1.2; }
```

```
a { height: 100px; }
